    "body" : "<p>For those who are facing this issue with \"Run\" window they can follow below instruction<br><br>\nFrom dropdown select \"Edit Configuration\":<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/LbaBB.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/LbaBB.png\" alt=\"From dropdown select &quot;Edit Configuration&quot;\"></a><br>\nOpen Logs tab:<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/aKc0Y.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/aKc0Y.png\" alt=\"Open Logs tab\"></a><br>\nUncheck these 2 checkboxes:<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/5sQmD.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/5sQmD.png\" alt=\"Uncheck these 2 checkboxes\"></a></p>\n"
